data.description: Welcome to the perfect blend of country living and convenience! This stunning property offers a unique opportunity to embrace the restfulness of rural life while remaining just a stone's throw away from town. Nestled on 5 acres of land, this beautiful and spacious 4/3 modular home from Clayton Homes is a true gem. Perfect setting for a farm lifestyle, with the already established setup, complete with goats, chickens, and even an adorable alpaca! The outdoor space is a haven for relaxation and entertainment. The interior is spacious with an open layout creating warmth and tranquility.
